Super Scarlet Universe
Malcolm Keith & Ralph Renz Castillo

Using player controller, user will navigate 5 different and uniqely built levels equipped with its own obstacles and enemies
Player will collect coins and power ups along the way in an attempt to reach the final boss on the final level taking place in the Rutgers 
fooball stadium. Player must collect all four diamonds on each level before being able to proceed to the next level. 

Assets include:
media from - https://www.assetstore.unity3d.com/en/
backgrounds from - https://www.google.com/imghp?hl=en&tab=wi&authuser=0 & https://opengameart.org/content/static-2d-backgrounds
other resources from the 2d source folder provided by the professor

Scripts provided by unity
Scripts also provided by https://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/topics/2d-game-creation/player-controller-script

